Lunar! ← ⍜∩(⇌-@0°⋕)^0      # binary lunar op
☾      ← Lunar!⬚0↥          # add
☽      ← Lunar!(/(☾˜⊂0)⊞↧)  # multiply

{976_348 23_321 232_35 [123 32192 415 8]}
∵◇(&p $"_ sum = _, product = _"⟜⊃/☾/☽)

&p "\nFirst 20 distinct even:"
&p ⇌◴⍢(⊂☽2⊸⧻|<20⧻◴)[]

&p "\nFirst 20 squares:"
&p ∵☽.⇡20

&p "\nFirst 20 factorials:"
&p ≡(/☽+1⇡)↘1⇡21

&p "\nFirst square smaller than previous:"
&p ⊙◌⍢∩+₁(<∩(☽.))1 0
